OL,7,FThe government says the proposals are
OL,8,Faimed at providing "more tailored
OL,9,Fsupport in line with their needs" but
OL,10,Fopposition MPs and charities have hit
OL,11,Fout at the plans.
OL,13,FScope called them a "reckless assault"
OL,14,Fon disabled people, while Mind urged
OL,15,Fthe government to "stop blaming people
OL,16,Fwith mental health problems" for being
OL,17,Fon benefits, insisting they don't
OL,18,Fchoose to be so, rather "it's their
OL,19,Flast resort".
