OL,7,FThe plans, which will be consulted on
OL,8,Fover the coming months, also include
OL,9,Fproposals to "move away from a fixed
OL,10,Fcash benefit system", meaning people
OL,11,Fwith some conditions will no longer
OL,12,Freceive regular payments but rather
OL,13,Fimproved access to treatment if their
OL,14,Fcondition does not involve extra costs.
OL,16,FThe government hopes the overall
OL,17,Fimpact will be to move to a system
OL,18,Fwhere PIP is more geared towards
OL,19,Fcovering the actual extra costs faced
OL,20,Fby people with disabilities.
