OL,7,FIn response to being asked whether
OL,8,Fthose suffering from anxiety would
OL,9,Flose benefits, the prime minister told
OL,10,FITV News Political Editor Robert
OL,11,FPeston that he wants to reform the PIP
OL,12,Fassessment system which he says is
OL,13,F"often easily exploited and subject to
OL,14,Funverifiable claims".
OL,16,F"What I want is to move towards
OL,17,Fsomething that is more rigorous, more
OL,18,Fobjective, and potentially has more
OL,19,Fmedical evidence that needs to be
OL,20,Fprovided when people are making those
OL,21,Fclaims," he said.
