OL,7,FWhen pressed further on those with
OL,8,Fanxiety, the PM said: "The broad
OL,9,Fthrust of what we're trying to do is
OL,10,Fsay, hang on, you can't be making
OL,11,Fclaims based on unverifiable
OL,12,Fassertions.
OL,14,F"There needs to be some objective
OL,15,Fevidence, perhaps medical, so that we
OL,16,Fcan say you are genuinely someone
OL,17,Fwho's in need of support."
