OL,7,F"Life costs a lot more for disabled
OL,8,Fpeople, including people with mental
OL,9,Fhealth conditions. Threatening to take
OL,10,Faway the low amount of income PIP
OL,11,Fprovides won't solve the country's
OL,12,Fproblems."
OL,14,FMind said "lots of the rhetoric"
OL,15,Faround mental health in politics
OL,16,Frecently "has been stigmatising,
OL,17,Fharmful and inaccurate," adding; "It's
OL,18,Fvery distressing, and for some of us
OL,19,Ftriggering, to hear mental health
OL,20,Fproblems used as a political football."
