OL,7,FThe number of monthly PIP awards for
OL,8,Fmental health disorders has doubled
OL,9,Fsince 2019, from 2,200 to 5,300, in
OL,10,Fline with an increase in overall PIP
OL,11,Fawards which have also doubled to
OL,12,F33,000 a month.
OL,14,FThe work and pensions secretary
OL,15,Fearlier said the system should not be
OL,16,Fpaying people to deal with the
OL,17,F"ordinary difficulties of life" and
OL,18,Fsuggested that many voters "deep down"
OL,19,Fagree with him.
